緊咩？<br />\n自以為好 high，其實極 low。 智商超過70既唔該檢討下。<br />\n<br />\n  #現場根本阻止唔到<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/g9uH5ri.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fg9uH5ri.jpg&h=730b6107&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T17:42:11.000Z","msg":"等送頭， 做既野同係佔旺嘉年華真心差唔多"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:06:25.000Z","msg":"日撚日都有班人將抗爭Spin 去嘉年華<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n只能夠講好多人都心靈唔夠強大<br />\n偶然需要呢啲心靈鴉片先行到落去<br />\n<br />\n就好似希特拉需要華格納嘅音樂咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要帶住呢班比較軟弱嘅和理非豬一齊行埋落去呀<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n利申：人人都會有軟弱暫時變豬嘅一刻，包括我<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ec80840837afa283fb4e9329a6f346284d6f32f3","tid":1755724,"uid":61886,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:07:26.000Z","msg":"仲唱肥媽果啲得3種<br />\n1. 小學生<br />\n2. 智商70或以下<br />\n3. on9仔"},{"pid":"a77f5a280fccbbacf3c32aa2b75ff3979a8213da","tid":1755724,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"咁既然大家講到個問題，有無推薦既歌？"},{"pid":"918d6b9e780af960cacd7100c775ee6157157a8c","tid":1755724,"uid":270374,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"a77f5a280fccbbacf3c32aa2b75ff3979a8213da","tid":1755724,"uid":320074,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:09:09.000Z","msg":"咁既然大家講到個問題，有無推薦既歌？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-26T03:13:03.000Z","msg":"仲唱歌，你有無病<br />\n最多只能唱榮光<br />\n<br />\n但係理大，有人被禁錮<br />\n當佢哋係背景自己開P就點都唔得"},{"pid":"00a4c170744d2bf664b6eebdcc0d47b94267f228","tid":1755724,"uid":270374,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"44421acc4cc48e7ee9e820f4bce7cf42b122eccc","tid":1755724,"uid":282490,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"0b702c7e6abd18d2253d7463247e3250bb3c9a94","tid":1755724,"uid":299991,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"495ae3d6952a929b89b3c186ed513ec847e98267","tid":1755724,"uid":270374,"like"